  "english": {
    "sections": [
      {
        "key": "statement",
        "title": "Statement",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "There is an N × M chessboard. You need to place K distinct rooks on this chessboard. The placement must satisfy all of the following conditions:"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "1. Each cell contains at most one rook."
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "2. Every row of the chessboard contains at least one rook."
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "3. Every column of the chessboard contains at least one rook."
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "Please find the total number of valid placements. Since the answer may be very large, you only need to output the result modulo 998244353."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "input",
        "title": "Input",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "The input contains only one line. This line contains three integers N, M, K in order (1 ≤ N, M, K ≤ $10^{5}$ ), representing the number of rows and columns of the chessboard, and the number of rooks to place, respectively."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "output",
        "title": "Output",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "Output one line containing an integer, the number of valid placements modulo 998244353."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "chinese": {
    "sections": [
      {
        "key": "statement",
        "title": "题目描述",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "有一个N×M的棋盘。你需要在这个棋盘上放置K个互不相同的“车”（即不同的棋子）。放置方案必须满足以下所有条件："
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "1.每个格子至多放置一个“车”。"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "2.棋盘的每一行都至少有一个“车”。"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "3.棋盘的每一列都至少有一个“车”。"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "请你求出满足条件的放置方案总数。由于答案可能很大，你只需要输出方案数对998244353取模后的结果。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "input",
        "title": "输入格式",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "输入仅包含一行。这一行依次包含三个整数N,M,K（1≤N,M,K≤$10^{5}$），分别表示棋盘的行数、列数以及需要放置的“车”的数量。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "output",
        "title": "输出格式",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "输出一行包含一个整数，表示合法的放置方案总数对998244353取模后的结果。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
